Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:53.85,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}改变了每天都一样的生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:57.38,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}微笑的魔法
